social_posts.post_text: Goofin around
Sketchin some more 90s heroes

I was lucky enough to do a few designs for My Dad the Bounty Hunter. I can’t say enough good things about Ev, Pat, Alex, and Yuhki!  They put together an amazing team and it shows.  I would leap at the chance to work with them again!  I hope you guys enjoy the show🤘🤖🤘
Hey, Gremlins came out!  I was so excited to do a bit of early development sketches for the show.  I wish I got to play around more on this show it was so fun.  Here are a few sketches I did.
More Gremlins stuff, some sketches of peeps in the market.
More Gremlins stuff, some sketches of peeps in the market.  I had a lot of fun with these.
